<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-07-1420 </DOCNO><TEXT>The results of study of the Halley comet by means of the ''Vega'', ''Suisej'',''Sakigaki'' and ''Jotton'' space probes are presented in the popularform. The form and composition of the comet nucleus, its atmosphere andprocesses ocurring when moving in the near-the-solar space are described.</TEXT></DOC>